Capital Markets

Company Overview of Nomura Asset Management Taiwan Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ING Securities Investment & Trust Company Limited was formerly known as ING CHB Securities Investment & Trust Co. Ltd. ING Securities Investment & Trust Co. Ltd. is based in Taiwan. As of April 18, 2014, ING Securities Investment & Trust Company Limited operates as a subsidiary of Nomura Asset Management Co., Ltd. and Allshores Group.


No 7 Xinyi Road30F,30-1F,31-1FSection 5Taipei,  Taiwan



Phone: 886 2 8101 5501

Fax: 886 2 8101 5597








